93
00:06:30,861 --> 00:06:41,471
[SPEAKER_11]: Applicant and owner are requesting a modification for the relief granted by the zoning board of appeals recorded by the city clerk on July 30th, 2021, as an extension granted by the zoning board on January 5th, 2023.

94
