767
01:08:24,324 --> 01:08:41,395
[SPEAKER_00]: The only people that come in contact with any of this jolt of current are those that are trespassing and have already breached the perimeter fence, so they've already breached the first line of security, which is their perimeter chain link fence, and then they come in contact with our fence.

768
01:08:44,428 --> 01:08:54,132
