769
01:08:54,452 --> 01:09:00,575
[SPEAKER_00]: You see one fence and ours kind of homogenizes with that perimeter chain link fence.

770
01:09:01,075 --> 01:09:06,417
[SPEAKER_00]: We don't alter the layout of the property or again, we don't alter the ingress or the egress.

771
01:09:07,557 --> 01:09:14,381
[SPEAKER_00]: our fence does need to be two feet taller than the non-electrified perimeter fence.

772
01:09:14,881 --> 01:09:16,863
[SPEAKER_00]: So that chain link fence is eight feet.

773
01:09:17,263 --> 01:09:24,467
[SPEAKER_00]: We need to be two feet taller because if we were the same height, there is a height slide in the attachments.

774
