789
01:10:49,488 --> 01:11:01,278
[SPEAKER_00]: The good thing about that is if you have a power outage, then the property is still protected because they are not on the mains grid, so they still have their alarm system that protects their property.

790
01:11:02,112 --> 01:11:07,655
[SPEAKER_00]: It's 12 volt battery charged by solar panel doesn't not carry continuous current.

791
01:11:08,056 --> 01:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_00]: Therefore, somebody doesn't latch on when they, if somebody were to touch our fence, they're not going to latch on like that.

792
01:11:15,160 --> 01:11:17,321
