1268
01:53:21,198 --> 01:53:28,281
[SPEAKER_03]: It's not very, like, it's not a visual eyesore from my assessment.

1269
01:53:29,661 --> 01:53:39,205
[SPEAKER_03]: So, yeah, I think in that sense, the fence height one, it pretty clearly meets the statutory criteria.

1270
01:53:39,225 --> 01:53:43,887
[SPEAKER_03]: It doesn't, you know, derogate from the intent of the ordinance.

1271
01:53:47,530 --> 01:53:58,203
[SPEAKER_03]: I don't really like being put in the position of having to decide whether to waive a security requirement.

1272
01:53:58,363 --> 01:54:06,432
[SPEAKER_03]: I do think that the final security plan that was submitted is very comprehensive.

1273
01:54:09,516 --> 01:54:12,478
[SPEAKER_03]: Not that pages is the best metric, but it's a good proxy.

1274
01:54:12,538 --> 01:54:19,443
[SPEAKER_03]: It's more than 59 pages long with scientific studies and other details.

1275
01:54:20,004 --> 01:54:24,587
[SPEAKER_03]: Everything I could think of to ask and assess is basically in here or I asked it today.

1276
01:54:26,869 --> 01:54:28,290
[SPEAKER_03]: And so I think it would be,

1277
01:54:30,852 --> 01:54:42,838
[SPEAKER_03]: you know, not a good experience for the applicant if this issue in the ordinance and the police chief's position, you know, made it an impossibility to install something like this.

1278
01:54:42,918 --> 01:54:49,901
[SPEAKER_03]: I think in general, you know, the obvious vectors to injure somebody, you know, have been addressed.

1279
01:54:50,301 --> 01:54:57,064
[SPEAKER_03]: Someone touching the fence, they're not going to get electrocuted because the perimeter fence is not electrocuted, it's just above.

1280
01:54:58,845 --> 01:55:03,428
[SPEAKER_03]: Even the wildlife, it seems like there's some mechanisms to avoid electrocuting them.

1281
01:55:04,469 --> 01:55:10,474
[SPEAKER_03]: The fire department has an industry standard way to access the site.

1282
01:55:11,154 --> 01:55:14,797
[SPEAKER_03]: And even if someone touches it, it seems like it's non-lethal.

1283
01:55:14,837 --> 01:55:15,937
[SPEAKER_03]: It's just uncomfortable.

1284
01:55:16,078 --> 01:55:27,526
[SPEAKER_03]: So in that sense, I think all of the things that a non-expert might ask pertaining to the safety, I think have been adequately addressed in this plan.

