1479
02:10:39,878 --> 02:10:47,040
[SPEAKER_12]: You know, once the configuration of the parking changes, then I felt as though this triggered off the need for a, an increase.

1480
02:10:48,369 --> 02:10:54,775
[SPEAKER_12]: in intensity of use and would require a special permit under the ordinance section in chapter six.

1481
02:10:55,335 --> 02:11:10,310
