1484
02:11:18,992 --> 02:11:29,514
[SPEAKER_12]: Um, the permit was issued legally and that, um, you know, that the burden didn't fall completely on, um, on the bill and inspector, because I just wanted to make sure that the T's were crossed and the I's were dotted.

1485
02:11:29,534 --> 02:11:37,816
[SPEAKER_12]: This is not a major violation or a major increase in, in, um, you know, in impact or configuration.

1486
02:11:37,856 --> 02:11:40,577
[SPEAKER_12]: They did it on their own property, but, uh, but I thought it would,

1487
02:11:41,578 --> 02:11:54,747
